<i>verb</i>: 벌어지다 [버ː러지다], 바라지다 [바ː라지다], 넓히다 [널피다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt>벌어지다 [버ː러지다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. widen</dd><br>
<dd>틈이나 간격 등이 생기다.</dd><br>
<dd>For a crack, space, etc., to form.</dd><br>
<dd>2. grow</dd><br>
<dd>식물의 잎이나 가지 등이 넓게 퍼져서 활짝 열리다.</dd><br>
<dd>For the leaf, branch, etc., of a plant to grow wider and longer.</dd><br>
<dd>3. be wide; be broad</dd><br>
<dd>어깨나 등, 가슴이 넓다.</dd><br>
<dd>For a shoulder, back, or chest to be wide.</dd><br>
<dd>4. (banquet) be given</dd><br>
<dd>음식 등을 번듯하게 차리다.</dd><br>
<dd>To set food, etc., generously for a certain occasion.</dd><br>
<dd>5. get wider</dd><br>
<dd>차이가 커지다.</dd><br>
<dd>For a difference to become bigger.</dd><br>
<dd>6. distance; become far; become uncomfortable</dd><br>
<dd>사람들 사이의 관계가 멀어지거나 불편해지다.</dd><br>
<dd>For a relationship between people to become distant or uncomfortable.</dd><br>
<dt>바라지다 [바ː라지다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. widen; have a crack</dd><br>
<dd>틈이나 간격 등이 생기다.</dd><br>
<dd>For a crack, space, etc., to form.</dd><br>
<dd>2. be broad</dd><br>
<dd>어깨나 등, 가슴이 넓다.</dd><br>
<dd>For a shoulder, back, or chest to be wide.</dd><br>
<dt>넓히다 [널피다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. broaden; widen</dd><br>
<dd>면이나 바닥 등의 면적을 크게 하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To enlarge a certain area such as the side or surface of something.</dd><br>
<dd>2. widen</dd><br>
<dd>폭을 길게 하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Make something wider.</dd><br>
<dd>3. become broad-minded</dd><br>
<dd>마음이나 생각을 크고 너그럽게 하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To expand one's mind or thoughts, and become broad-minded</dd><br>
<dd>4. expand; widen; broaden</dd><br>
<dd>내용이나 범위를 널리 미치게 하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To make the content or scope of something cover wider areas.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>